### Registrar postulante a diplomado (con documento académico PDF)
POST /api/diplomado/register
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="program_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="academic_period_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="full_name"

Juan Pérez García
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="dni"

12345678
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="birthdate"

1990-05-15
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="phone"

987654321
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="email"

juan.perez@example.com
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="address"

Av. Universitaria 1234
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="city"

Lima
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="university"

Universidad Nacional Mayor de San Marcos
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="academic_degree"

bachelor
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="career"

Ingeniería de Sistemas
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="academic_document"; filename="bachiller.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./bachiller.pdf
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="voucher_type"

boleta
------FormBoundary--


### Registrar postulante con factura
POST /api/diplomado/register
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="program_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="academic_period_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="full_name"

María López Torres
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="dni"

87654321
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="birthdate"

1985-03-22
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="phone"

912345678
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="email"

maria.lopez@empresa.com
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="address"

Jr. Los Pinos 456
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="city"

Arequipa
------FormBoundary
